title: Mozart - The Late Symphonies - Bernstein, VPO
description:
Mozart: The Late Symphonies (Nos. 25, 29, 35, 36, 38, 39, 40, and 41)

DG released this 3 disc collection of Bernstein conducting Mozart's late symphonies with the Vienna Philharmonic in 2003. The recordings come from the 1980s and are Romantic by the standards of contemporary, period performance standards. Nevertheless, they will satisfy anyone who loves these symphonies--the recordings of 40 and 41 are most likely the best I've heard.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
